responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "30586ECD4D6DE76472926EB4F83A0175", "[This is a brief review of the life and times of one Professor Olek Bellsong, an inventor and scholar of the ancient city of Carphin. It was made for his funeral. He was not a demigod, but rather, a simple Dunir immigrant. His specialty was the study of time and space. According to this, he vanished with his tower from a hill near the city of Aela, leaving a magical vortex and odd floating crystal in its place. A similar fate befell his apprentice mere months before! They were never seen again.]")
